Description: OpenSSL-based stdin/stdout crypto program (RSA seal/open and AES-256-CBC)
 A small CLI tool demonstrating OpenSSL EVP APIs:
 - rsa-enc / rsa-dec: hybrid RSA+AES sealing
 - aes-enc / aes-dec: AES-256-CBC with embedded key+iv container
